Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支持分期付款不用擔心現金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Take it easy see you next week
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們下周再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要2個麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不知道該怎麼吐槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小燦 你們組弄的減肥產品 全部都貢獻給我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要我做那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為本小姐的傭人 這不是當然的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是對你們的施捨 是  施 捨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦 在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你要開始減肥  我就把廣告商品拿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:08:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些全部都是我送你作禮物的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 謝謝爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豪仔好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦的東西就是我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多沒有見過的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人魚養命水？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這水能促進健康的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個！我想要的有氧運動的DVD
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點開始有氧運動吧 小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留奈還是老樣子  這麼強硬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無…無碼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠得到鍛煉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是無碼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為我的兒子 癖好不一般啊 色情狂永澄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  這個已經不是癖好不癖好的層次了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大 已經裝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回頭給你記上一功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\pos(360,260)}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.13,0:09:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是人魚減肥用的最尖端機械 室內「鯉躍龍門」機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在購買還附送桑拿室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴室你們愛怎麼樣就怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動手 鯊藤代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我按
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:09:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油！小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像鯉魚那樣急流勇進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水流好急
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,量那麼大 差點都被淹沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是減肥的一環
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當個有特殊癖好的人也無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼 工作以後蒸桑拿真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電視購物 主持人什麼的 並不適合我做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 你買了那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.27,0:10:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦 滿潮家今晚吃魚嗎？ 味道真香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全身清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣體重也下降了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 爸爸你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該減一減了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:54.96,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,metabolic(代謝失調)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被燦責備了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豪仔 shock！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒錯 這將軍肚可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就蒸桑拿減肥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 我還沒見過小燦的爸爸的人魚形態呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要偷看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實也沒啥嘛  大家都是男人 輕鬆輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在偷看什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋  竟然敢偷看我裸體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變態的毒蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太好色了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僕人很適合做極品小受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊 我並不是想看看小燦的爸爸的裸體…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄  原來你喜歡男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對啊 這是誤會啊 小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太神了 我還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是剛才說能促進健康的水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄 不能喝那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  什麼什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這人魚養命水 最適用於治療腰肩酸痛 滋養強身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這只限於人魚喝  聽說人類喝了會不得了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？ 是這樣啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄把人魚養命水一口喝光了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？！ 那是店裏所有存貨的濃縮液啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是海蟑螂 有夠無知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人魚的飲料被人喝了會發生什麼事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說這麼恐怖的話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死不了就行了 我去上個廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對兒子的事情這麼冷漠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼…啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 小燦 快逃到屋子外面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄巨大化了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄的爸爸呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的 我的35年按揭貸款啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燦小姐 那個巨大化的身體被人看到就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快唱那首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人魚古代歌詞 「睡眠之詩」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小鳥？是飛機？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謎之音：superman的經典台詞啊~ ~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.80,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,附近居民爆睡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燦小姐 這樣唱下去的話 連永澄也會睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼唱了這麼久 僕人還沒睡著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他喝了人魚養命水 已經變成和我們人魚相近的存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對人魚歌聲的抗性也上升了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他離人類越來越遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 喝了那水連自我意識都失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「那裏」變得很精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,快躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 小巡學姐好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更新了50米個人最佳成績
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好球！ 出局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做人可能一直都太認真了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:36.49,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,謎之音：she say…很嚴重的低級語法錯誤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽 給我買副新眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 沒見一會 我家兒子都長得這麼大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.03,0:15:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 媽媽 請快點照看一下爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我對這個脫掉內褲還鼾然大睡的男人做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百年之戀也要醒悟過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 燦小姐 永澄要開始暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想想辦法阻止他的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到有可能會發生這種事 今天把他帶過來是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除人類狀態 變回原來的樣子吧 蛸中島
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,章魚到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛸 就這樣把他壓制住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不就變成怪獸戰鬥了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,章~魚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛸竟然敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還是毫無怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算玩過家家也不要玩得這麼過分啊 永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了 這樣下去永澄要破壞城鎮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦 就包在我身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這聲音是 海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦仰角最大「海王丸」緊急上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上浮 請注意 上浮 請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我兒子的命根…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了吧 滿潮永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等我來消滅你這個寡廉鮮恥的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄的怒火已經讓他完全忘記了自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他繼續鬧下去可是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主 少主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動作真快 猿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經把宇宙穿梭機準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮！猿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切準備工作都做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是發射按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 快退下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我接上熱線 這邊的準備工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:45.63,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,別碰 永澄的秘密BOX 我死了以後請把它燒掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經萬無一失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主引擎 準備啟動 倒數5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 這樣就可以安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦 你就放棄永澄吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜點啊 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個稍微借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 這樣就接上了衛星回路了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還活著呢 在月球上鬧著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦 雖然很遺憾 事到如今 只能放棄永澄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我也很傷心難過 但你就放手去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來把滿潮永澄滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海 你也住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,軍事衛星導彈同時發射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,導彈很快就到達 直接命中滿潮永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧 滿潮永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝酒慶祝啊 給我拿酒來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼驚人的生命力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄在哭 為了他所深愛的地球在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謎之音：明顯就是為了那箱子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 就沒有其他方法能救到永澄了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經無能為力了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦 雖然我能理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我在倒著飛 小燦果然還是很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了 小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忙著加班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 在保健室的窗口看到永澄的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我喝的那口咖啡全噴出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這把是名槍「涅府血游吽」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名槍 涅府血游吽\N為身體的異常感到煩惱的各位\N現向你們推薦\N向你們推薦\N涅府血游吽\N擁有使身體恢復正常的\N淨化之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能把身體的異常情況回復到正常 隱藏著「淨化」的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼時候弄得這把東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是我們的廣告商品嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由於現在是深夜 請不要撥錯號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好沉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這槍投出去 貫穿永澄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其重量等於你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想救永澄的心 會變成淨化的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對永澄的思念 會變成淨化的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到月亮的距離 還有槍的重量 都毫無關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連丈夫都救不了的話  到底算哪門子妻子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要 救出永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫是寫作「仁俠」  但讀作「人魚」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳達吧 我的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滯空時間有夠久的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,章魚~ ~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,章魚~ ~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了這種情況 我們為您特別附送多一把
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電話號碼是 0120…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫是寫作「仁俠」  但讀作「人魚」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謎之音：果然是朗O努斯之槍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄 妻子在地球等著你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你一定要平安無事地回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 永澄的呼吸停了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿政
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來人工呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄 永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦…咦 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太好了 燦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 小燦 我一切都記得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次不夠 還來了第二次…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 其實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實呢 我是想親自來人工呼吸的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是我的僕人 賊運亨通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 永澄 你都記得啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.39,0:21:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不用在說明什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還我家來 你這混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子他爸  幫這種兒子付醫療費實在愚蠢之極 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦 現在房子毀了就搬到我家去住吧 最好住一輩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心我廢了你 三河
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,35年的按揭貸款就你來付啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回月亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天要早起 幹活又要干到深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.87,0:23:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶像這份職業果然夠累人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.49,0:23:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以假日裏想好好休息也可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿著睡衣滑到也可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.25,0:23:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是留奈 不要告訴我那麼殘酷的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.37,0:23:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要奪去我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.36,0:23:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫是寫作「愛的奴隸」 但讀作「偶像」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:41.95,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H000000&\3c&Hffffff&\shad0}{\an8}愛的奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.69,0:23:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是夠苦的
